data.text: @vincentdesmond_ Didn’t you see Shangela on AS3? Who better for a Mariah tribute? 😩
@vincentdesmond_ Jessie J would be perfect for Celine
@vincentdesmond_ Ariana would be perfect but I feel like Mariah would wake up from the dead if we let Ariana sing a tribute to her, just to be petty. I kinda want Shakira for Celine though.
@demiggys She remains one of my favorite vocalists. Exactly, Demi is so talented and she can convey emotions, something Celine's songs need.
@demiggys Leona's voice isn't what it used to be, it's better than most but not as magical as it once was which is sad. Oh true about that Celine bit I guess.
